OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thu 12 Mar to Sat 21 Mar
OL,6,FThis period will continue to see the
OL,7,FUK located at the interface between
OL,8,Fhigh pressure across Europe and low
OL,9,Fpressure over the North Atlantic. As
OL,10,Fsuch, north western areas will likely
OL,11,Fsee the focus of spells of rain at
OL,12,Ftimes, along with stronger winds,
OL,13,Fwhereas south eastern parts should see
OL,14,Fmore in the way of drier interludes,
OL,15,Fthough even here, some rain is
OL,16,Fexpected from time to time.
OL,17,FTemperatures should overall be a
OL,18,Flittle above average for most areas,
OL,19,Fthough there are likely to be times
OL,20,Fwhen it will be cooler too, bringing a
OL,21,Frisk of overnight frosts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
