OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sun 22 Mar to Sun 5 AprFThe
OL,6,Fstart of this period could see
OL,7,Funsettled conditions fairly widely
OL,8,Facross the UK, with spells of rain and
OL,9,Fstrong winds affecting many areas at
OL,10,Ftimes, although western areas likely
OL,11,Fremain wettest. Then, whilst
OL,12,Fconfidence in the details is low,
OL,13,Fthere is the potential for weather
OL,14,Fpatterns to become slower-moving by
OL,15,Flate March, bringing more settled and
OL,16,Fdrier conditions . Overall,
OL,17,Ftemperatures will probably end up near
OL,18,Fto average, though there are
OL,19,Findications of a cooler spell near the
OL,20,Fturn of the month.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
